01:07:50,800 --> 01:07:54,133
- Ya, masuklah.
- Ceritakan tentang Wardell Fouse.

1074
01:07:54,216 --> 01:07:55,674
Fouse?

1075
01:07:55,758 --> 01:07:57,758
Kau percaya omong kosong itu
sekarang?

